order.name: Cookies and Cream Protein Minis (No Added Sugar)
order.description: Experience delight with our Ice Cream Protein Bars! These stickless treats redefine indulgence, blending chocolatey goodness with a creamy ice cream center. The classic combination of indulgent cookies and rich creamy ice cream with a delightful crunch of cookie crumbs, packs 5g protein, 125 kcal, and is naturally sweetened. #Flexyoursweettooth
